PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST by updating the reference to a departmental publication entitled « A Guide to Canada's Export Controls » so that it refers to the latest edition published in December 2005, and by replacing all of item 5202 concerning unprocessed roe herring so that it reflects both Canada's international and multilateral commitments and its export policy.
